@node Mercenary1 "Mercenary: Escape from Targ & The Second City"

"Escape from Targ" saved games are called Mercenary1.save?
"The Second City"  saved games are called Mercenary2.save?
where ? represents a number from 0 to 9.

In the game, numeric ENTER will load a game, and Esc will save it.
