@node TVSports "TV Sports Baseball/Basketball/Boxing/Football"

@{b}TV Sports Baseball@{ub}

This game is also known as "Bo Jackson Baseball".
  This game has a built-in team editor; we suggest using that instead of
MCE ;-) .
